The paper proposes a new framework for mitigating biases in machine learning systems using conditional Generative Adversarial Networks (cGANs). This work involves techniques related to machine learning, artificial intelligence, computer vision, and data analysis. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
